node.text: As followers will be aware, Wilfred has a new obsession; this weed/plant that is growing around the drain in the back yard. He has regular visitations to the plant during the day, to examine and inspect it's progress. This is Wilfred checking his plant.

node.text: I saw that tiktok wall challenge cat intelligence test and couldn't wait to try it on Wilfred 🤣 According to the test, if the cat holds out their arms outstretched to prevent them going into the wall then they get 10/10. If they allow themselves to be smushed into the wall then they score 0/10. I feel Wilfred scored a solid 5 😸
